WEBVTT

01:38.400 --> 01:40.520
EPISODE 12

01:43.080 --> 01:46.600
ZHIYI TECH

01:46.680 --> 01:49.080
- This is your office?
- Yes.

01:55.840 --> 01:57.880
It's Sunday. No one's here.

02:04.680 --> 02:05.680
Come on in.

02:24.440 --> 02:26.320
Isn't this Puppet Master
from "A Chinese Ghost Story"?

02:26.920 --> 02:29.720
Yes. Come here.

02:40.680 --> 02:43.080
- This is...
- My office.

02:45.520 --> 02:48.760
- Can you study here?
- Sure.

02:58.840 --> 03:00.040
I'll get started then.

03:01.160 --> 03:02.640
I have work to do, too.

03:21.160 --> 03:22.920
It's so quiet.

03:23.480 --> 03:27.160
But it's a little too quiet.
I can't absorb anything.

03:27.720 --> 03:30.080
I can't believe I'm alone with Lord.

03:38.880 --> 03:39.720
Weiwei?

03:42.000 --> 03:42.920
Come take a look at this.

03:50.320 --> 03:51.520
What's this?

03:51.720 --> 03:53.920
Basic character design
for our mobile game.

03:55.480 --> 03:58.480
- Your mobile game?
- Yes.

04:00.120 --> 04:01.240
Take a look.

04:37.400 --> 04:38.880
I like this game.

04:42.280 --> 04:43.200
Just from character design?

04:44.600 --> 04:48.040
You can tell a lot from character design.

04:52.000 --> 04:55.640
Female characters in
online games nowadays

04:55.720 --> 04:58.680
tend to wear next to nothing.
Some are practically naked,

04:59.240 --> 05:01.120
just to entice male players.

05:01.760 --> 05:04.600
I picked the swordswoman in red

05:04.680 --> 05:07.040
for her skill set,

05:07.120 --> 05:09.440
and also because she's very covered up.

05:10.960 --> 05:13.320
Your game isn't like that.

05:13.400 --> 05:16.280
The outfits on the female characters
are all very normal.

05:17.320 --> 05:21.560
That shows the game designers
are confident in their work

05:21.800 --> 05:23.800
and have respect for their game.

05:23.880 --> 05:27.120
They're not using frivolous methods
to please the masses.

05:27.280 --> 05:30.040
Thanks for the compliment.
I'm very honored.

05:33.120 --> 05:35.160
Lord seems to be in a good mood.

05:35.240 --> 05:38.120
Did I butter him up by accident?

05:38.640 --> 05:39.800
When is the alpha test?

05:40.560 --> 05:42.080
End of the year, at the earliest.

05:43.680 --> 05:44.520
I want an alpha test account.

05:45.720 --> 05:48.960
- Well...
- I can't have one?

05:50.200 --> 05:53.320
It depends on our favorability
of each other then.

05:53.960 --> 05:55.680
Lord is so...

05:56.120 --> 05:58.240
It depends on our favorability?

05:58.320 --> 06:01.480
No, I can't let him
get the last word all the time.

06:02.280 --> 06:04.320
How does one increase favorability?

06:05.360 --> 06:07.120
I'll come up with a calculation model.

06:14.480 --> 06:19.040
By the way, what did you mean by
complicated,

06:19.120 --> 06:20.880
when I mentioned
Fengteng's offer to buy our video?

06:23.440 --> 06:26.800
Our company is likely to collaborate
with Fengteng on this mobile game,

06:26.880 --> 06:30.480
as well as a joint project to develop
"A New Chinese Ghost Story."

06:31.360 --> 06:32.240
"A New Chinese Ghost Story"?

06:33.560 --> 06:36.080
Yes, it hasn't been announced yet.

06:37.560 --> 06:39.240
Since you know them,

06:39.320 --> 06:41.800
why don't you handle the video matter?

06:41.880 --> 06:43.160
That's really the best.

06:43.240 --> 06:45.440
The video was released under my name,

06:45.520 --> 06:46.720
but you were the one who made it.

06:48.040 --> 06:48.960
Let's not sell it, then.

06:50.280 --> 06:53.320
If you don't end up working with them,
we can save the idea for ourselves.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.920
Don't mind that.
You should just sign the contract.

06:59.960 --> 07:01.920
Okay, I'll sign it,

07:02.000 --> 07:03.880
and split the licensing fee five ways.

07:05.800 --> 07:06.960
Don't give it to Yugong and the others.

07:08.840 --> 07:10.920
Wouldn't that be wrong?
They took part, too.

07:11.320 --> 07:14.640
Just keep it,
as their first-meeting gift to you.

07:21.200 --> 07:24.440
I was going to ask him
what I should do about his cut.

07:24.520 --> 07:26.240
Now, I guess that's moot.

07:26.440 --> 07:28.440
What if he said,
take it as a betrothal gift?

07:34.120 --> 07:35.920
I thought that was weird.

07:36.000 --> 07:37.760
Why was he standing over there?

07:37.960 --> 07:40.200
It's because I'm in his seat.

08:02.960 --> 08:04.360
"A Chinese Ghost Story"
limited edition mug?

08:05.120 --> 08:06.000
That's yours.

08:11.560 --> 08:14.760
There are more, right?
There are 20 characters in total.

08:14.840 --> 08:16.720
There must be 20 mugs?

08:17.720 --> 08:19.680
Fengteng gave us a set.

08:19.880 --> 08:20.880
I only took these two.

08:21.520 --> 08:23.280
Yugong and the others have the rest.

08:26.040 --> 08:28.880
So he saved the mug for me?

08:29.320 --> 08:33.000
He knew I'd come to his office
sooner or later.

08:34.760 --> 08:36.159
Xiao Nai...

08:38.039 --> 08:40.159
How did you recognize me that day?

08:42.720 --> 08:43.720
Xiao Nai?

08:49.600 --> 08:52.280
At Acme, in March.

08:55.200 --> 08:56.040
The internet cafe?

08:58.280 --> 09:00.240
I was there for a meeting,

09:00.520 --> 09:03.520
and I saw you battling someone
on my way out.

09:06.720 --> 09:09.880
So Lord knew me
back then already.

09:10.960 --> 09:13.640
Your maneuvering was great
and your hand speed rapid.

09:18.600 --> 09:20.120
I was a quality control tester

09:20.200 --> 09:23.920
during the summer of my 12th grade year,
and that's how I trained.

09:24.040 --> 09:27.680
My APM wasn't high,
usually less than 150.

09:28.880 --> 09:31.040
APM is only a reference point.

09:33.640 --> 09:37.480
Compared to APM, perhaps effective
maneuver rate is more critical.

09:38.000 --> 09:43.280
What's your APM, Lord?

09:43.600 --> 09:47.280
I've never tested. When I started playing,
there was no concept of APM.

09:48.840 --> 09:51.000
No concept of APM?

09:51.160 --> 09:53.120
How long ago was that?

09:53.960 --> 09:57.560
Lord must be super dreamy
when he's playing.

09:58.200 --> 10:00.880
Why don't we battle?

10:02.040 --> 10:04.360
Sure, but miss...

10:06.400 --> 10:07.520
Take it easy on me.

10:08.120 --> 10:10.680
Why do I get the feeling that
where he paused,

10:10.760 --> 10:13.160
he was going to say
"missus, take it easy on me"?

10:13.840 --> 10:15.560
I must be going mad today.

10:16.160 --> 10:17.520
I'll study now.

10:24.960 --> 10:27.280
He knew me for months already.

10:27.480 --> 10:30.040
Why didn't he say so in the game?

10:30.240 --> 10:32.880
We saw each other
in archaeology class, too.

10:33.560 --> 10:34.520
Wait, no.

10:34.880 --> 10:37.920
I've taken his class, too.
You don't have to say nice things for him.

10:38.800 --> 10:42.080
Yeah, I sat next to you once.

10:43.600 --> 10:44.520
I know.

10:47.000 --> 10:50.080
So, that's what that meant!

10:53.680 --> 10:54.520
Weiwei...

10:56.880 --> 11:00.760
If you keep staring at me,
I won't be able to take it anymore.

11:13.280 --> 11:15.640
Roaming around the world,
you're bound to get knifed.

11:15.720 --> 11:17.880
Five stabs killing you, killing you...

11:17.960 --> 11:19.320
Hand it over.

11:22.720 --> 11:24.800
Enough... Switch...

11:24.880 --> 11:26.280
Bench player Hao Mei is up. Come on!

11:29.640 --> 11:30.480
Go on!

11:30.560 --> 11:32.200
- Fine, I'll do it myself.
- Sweet!

11:32.280 --> 11:34.400
I'll get the ball...

11:34.480 --> 11:36.200
Let me...

11:36.440 --> 11:39.000
- Go on!
- Nice shot!

11:39.520 --> 11:40.640
What's the meaning of this?

11:40.720 --> 11:42.280
You're supposed to be my friends!

11:42.360 --> 11:44.680
That one abandoned his buddy
to go on a date.

11:44.760 --> 11:47.240
You two treat your buddy,
me, like thin air.

11:47.320 --> 11:49.760
I worked hard to raise
the handsomeness of the dorm,

11:49.840 --> 11:51.920
and this is how you thank me?

11:52.000 --> 11:53.400
Pass! Shoot!

11:54.200 --> 11:56.360
Fine, this won't defeat

11:56.440 --> 11:59.120
the passion of a man. You just wait.

12:19.600 --> 12:21.680
Ladies and gentlemen...

12:22.080 --> 12:25.800
we bring you live coverage
of the hottest star soccer match.

12:25.880 --> 12:28.440
The arena stands are completely filled.

12:28.520 --> 12:31.560
The fans' roaring cheer
has drowned out Hao Mei.

12:33.360 --> 12:34.600
Now, the ball is passed to Hao Mei.

12:34.680 --> 12:38.720
Look at him, with a left kick,
a right kick, a slow-motion,

12:38.800 --> 12:40.040
he passes the opposition player.

12:43.720 --> 12:46.520
His movement is agile,
and his footwork rapid.

12:47.040 --> 12:49.920
In the blink of the eye,
he's past eight opposition players.

12:52.080 --> 12:53.400
Facing down the goalie,

12:54.120 --> 12:55.280
he shoots!

12:58.240 --> 13:00.400
- Enjoy.
- Thanks.

13:06.320 --> 13:09.000
I was so inefficient this afternoon.

13:09.160 --> 13:12.080
Why don't I go back to the dorm
after the meal?

13:37.440 --> 13:38.440
Do you want to battle me?

13:51.800 --> 13:53.560
Are you better now?

13:53.640 --> 13:57.040
I can't believe you caught a cold
on top of the acute gastroenteritis!

13:58.200 --> 13:59.640
Don't be so sickly.

13:59.720 --> 14:01.040
Take medicine for the cold.

14:01.280 --> 14:02.840
Here, I have some.

14:04.120 --> 14:05.560
I knew I could count on you.

14:05.760 --> 14:07.080
Those two with boyfriends

14:07.160 --> 14:08.880
are out on dates every weekend.

14:08.960 --> 14:11.000
I never get to see them.

14:12.680 --> 14:15.680
A friend in need is a friend indeed.

14:16.040 --> 14:19.960
Sisi, it'll just be the two of us
from now on.

14:20.040 --> 14:22.000
That's right, even when sick,

14:22.080 --> 14:25.560
you should still be happy.
Laughter cures all ills.

14:27.880 --> 14:32.840
Actually, Erxi,
I'm going to study with a boy.

14:32.920 --> 14:35.840
Why don't you hang out with your laptop?

14:35.920 --> 14:38.080
I should go!

14:39.280 --> 14:40.560
Sisi!

14:42.520 --> 14:46.240
Heartless... They all left me, one by one.

14:49.440 --> 14:54.200
No, I have to find my own
chicken soup for the soul.

15:19.240 --> 15:21.040
I'm sick.

15:21.120 --> 15:24.560
I feel awful and pitiful.

15:26.360 --> 15:29.240
You're online!
Where are you? I'll go to you.

15:31.560 --> 15:33.880
I'm at Mochou Lake, by Jinling City.

15:41.720 --> 15:42.800
Wait for me.

15:45.960 --> 15:46.840
Okay.

16:15.080 --> 16:16.560
What a gorgeous horse!

16:17.160 --> 16:18.600
It's a gift for you.

16:19.840 --> 16:21.160
Really? That's awesome!

16:23.320 --> 16:26.240
The horse must have cost you
a lot of money.

16:26.400 --> 16:28.920
This gift is too expensive.

16:29.000 --> 16:31.720
This horse is fast and loose.

16:32.360 --> 16:34.000
He has a long stride.

16:34.320 --> 16:37.400
So he runs very fast.
He's perfect for you.

16:39.120 --> 16:42.360
I love this horse,
whether he runs fast or not.

16:42.440 --> 16:44.400
I'll like it, as long as it's from you.

16:47.320 --> 16:48.960
Keep acting.

16:49.040 --> 16:51.080
I'd like to see how far you can push it.

16:51.160 --> 16:53.240
Two can play this game.

16:55.480 --> 16:57.680
- Do you want to go on a boat ride?
- Here?

16:57.760 --> 17:01.040
I didn't know
there are boat rides in the game.

17:01.600 --> 17:03.760
I saw a few boats on my way here.

17:03.840 --> 17:05.160
I'm sure we can do it.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.240
Sure.

17:19.800 --> 17:21.800
- I'll take two boats.
- Sure thing.

17:21.880 --> 17:25.040
Why two boats? We can just share one.

17:25.240 --> 17:27.400
Isn't it more fun with two boats?

17:27.480 --> 17:28.520
I think you'll like it.

17:30.520 --> 17:34.080
It implies two-timing. Don't you get it?

17:36.840 --> 17:39.560
That's true. We can race!

17:43.640 --> 17:46.240
I've got nothing on you, in that regard.

17:47.120 --> 17:49.360
Come on! Let's ride together.

18:44.560 --> 18:46.640
What are those flowers? So pretty.

18:50.400 --> 18:53.480
I'm guessing they're called
"wanton flowers."

18:54.560 --> 18:55.640
Why's that?

18:57.280 --> 18:59.800
Look at the willows on the shore.

18:59.880 --> 19:02.360
The flowers fall into the lake,
before they can blossom,

19:03.160 --> 19:05.680
but they don't give up on themselves.

19:05.880 --> 19:09.240
So they bloom into "wanton flowers."

19:10.720 --> 19:12.560
That's so poetic!

19:13.360 --> 19:17.800
Somehow, after your explanation,
these flowers seem so incredible.

19:18.920 --> 19:21.680
"Wanton flowers"
blossom for their own joy.

19:22.440 --> 19:24.960
That reminds of me the Little Prince's
vain and selfish flower.

19:27.840 --> 19:30.240
So you do know yourself.

19:32.680 --> 19:36.680
I used to think
it had negative connotations.

19:36.800 --> 19:41.600
Now, it feels quite pleasant
and inspiring.

20:04.840 --> 20:09.200
Weiguang, you never cease to amaze me.

20:23.280 --> 20:25.120
I want to give you a gift, too.

20:25.200 --> 20:27.760
It must be very special, very precious,

20:27.840 --> 20:30.400
so it can match the care
you have shown for me.

20:37.520 --> 20:39.440
Perfect timing, Weiwei!

20:40.440 --> 20:44.000
What's going on?
Why is your face so flushed?

20:44.080 --> 20:45.640
Do you have a fever?

20:45.880 --> 20:48.200
No fever...

20:48.280 --> 20:51.080
I just have a cold.
I took some medicine and got better.

20:52.840 --> 20:53.840
You came back just in time.

20:54.200 --> 20:57.680
If I want to give a friend
in the game a gift,

20:58.400 --> 21:01.640
and it should be a meaningful,
one-of-a-kind gift,

21:01.720 --> 21:02.880
what should I give him?

21:04.120 --> 21:05.240
You and I have the same idea!

21:05.800 --> 21:09.040
- You're giving Lord a gift?
- Yes.

21:11.640 --> 21:14.760
Erxi, did you also find someone...

21:14.840 --> 21:17.600
No way... I'm not like you.

21:18.840 --> 21:21.840
A friend in the game did me a huge favor.

21:21.920 --> 21:25.800
I only want to show gratitude. That's all.

21:26.760 --> 21:28.080
What are you giving Lord?

21:29.080 --> 21:31.440
I want to make him a gift.

21:32.040 --> 21:34.360
You're making it? What the heck?

21:35.680 --> 21:36.960
You've been gaming for a while.

21:37.040 --> 21:41.000
You don't know you can make
your own equipment and name it?

21:42.440 --> 21:45.840
I want to make him one,
but I still need two rare materials.

21:46.800 --> 21:47.960
You can do that?

21:48.440 --> 21:52.440
Yes, but making your own equipment
is very time-consuming.

21:52.520 --> 21:54.160
If you don't have time,

21:54.240 --> 21:57.240
you can consider other gifts.
I'll go wash my face.

21:59.720 --> 22:02.680
Make your own equipment?

22:44.480 --> 22:47.000
Men are all vindictive indeed.

22:47.680 --> 22:48.960
It's a good thing, though.

22:49.640 --> 22:52.160
Where are we going to get coffee, Yiran?

22:53.480 --> 22:55.240
- Same place.
- Okay.

22:55.560 --> 22:58.800
Why didn't you come back
to the dorm last night, Yiran?

22:58.880 --> 23:00.800
You didn't drink the juice I bought.

23:00.880 --> 23:02.760
I don't want to stay at the dorm.

23:03.520 --> 23:04.400
Why not?

23:04.480 --> 23:06.720
You love it here. Why won't you stay?

23:06.800 --> 23:09.560
- No reason.
- Let's go.

23:10.440 --> 23:11.840
I'll show you something.

23:15.120 --> 23:17.800
It's about Xiao Nai and Bei Weiwei.

23:18.880 --> 23:21.760
I'm not interested in them. Let's go.

23:24.920 --> 23:27.600
Fine, be that way. You'll regret it.

23:46.400 --> 23:47.720
This is my business card.

23:51.400 --> 23:53.400
- Hi, Mr. Liu.
- Hello.

23:53.480 --> 23:55.760
Our staff contacted you earlier.

23:55.840 --> 23:57.440
We'd like to use
"Girl Bandit Abducts Groom"

23:57.520 --> 23:59.120
in our official video campaign.

23:59.360 --> 24:01.920
Meanwhile, we'd like to incorporate

24:02.000 --> 24:03.320
the marriage by abduction plot
into the gameplay.

24:04.040 --> 24:06.240
I watched your video before I came.

24:06.320 --> 24:08.080
It's nicely done.
The plot is very original.

24:08.680 --> 24:10.440
It well deserves

24:10.520 --> 24:12.760
first place in the video contest.

24:13.320 --> 24:14.600
Thank you.

24:14.760 --> 24:17.960
- What can I get for you, sir?
- Just coffee. Thanks.

24:21.800 --> 24:24.640
Do you have any demand
for the compensation?

24:26.200 --> 24:27.880
I'd like to hear your offer.

24:28.720 --> 24:30.440
We're willing to pay 20,000 RMB

24:30.520 --> 24:32.040
for the right to use the video
for three years,

24:32.720 --> 24:35.360
including creative usage, of course.

24:37.520 --> 24:40.160
The game recently launched rare monsters.

24:41.120 --> 24:45.080
If I ask for rare monsters
in lieu of cash payment,

24:45.240 --> 24:47.520
- would that be possible?
- I think so.

24:47.600 --> 24:49.280
How many of which grades of rare monsters

24:49.360 --> 24:50.440
do you have in mind?

24:52.480 --> 24:55.040
I want five super rare monsters.

24:56.000 --> 25:00.080
Super rare monsters? Well...

25:00.800 --> 25:02.040
Enjoy.

25:04.480 --> 25:07.320
Ms. Bei, five super rare monsters

25:07.400 --> 25:09.240
are worth more than 20,000 RMB.

25:11.560 --> 25:13.800
To you guys, it's just data.

25:13.880 --> 25:15.240
Wouldn't that upset the balance?

25:15.320 --> 25:16.600
Our executives would never agree.

25:17.520 --> 25:18.800
Oh, no!

25:18.880 --> 25:22.240
I only want to give them
to my friends in the game.

25:23.160 --> 25:25.720
I'm sure you know, me and my friends

25:25.800 --> 25:27.880
all have high grades in the game.

25:28.240 --> 25:31.000
We'll get the best monsters
sooner or later.

25:31.360 --> 25:34.360
It can't upset the balance
that much, right?

25:35.600 --> 25:38.120
But if we release five at once,

25:38.200 --> 25:40.240
we still have to answer to other players.

25:42.160 --> 25:43.120
I'll tell you what, Ms. Bei,

25:43.480 --> 25:45.560
can you accept regular rare monsters?

25:56.840 --> 25:59.680
All right, I'll take
regular rare monsters,

26:00.240 --> 26:02.720
but I'd like two materials, as well.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.720
White jade and quenched metal.

26:06.160 --> 26:09.160
These two materials are rare reward items.

26:10.320 --> 26:11.480
Well...

26:15.400 --> 26:16.920
Since you're so straightforward,

26:17.000 --> 26:18.360
let's make that happen.

26:18.440 --> 26:19.640
I brought the contracts with me.

26:19.720 --> 26:21.760
I'll make changes to the terms.

26:37.240 --> 26:38.600
Take a look, Ms. Bei.

26:38.680 --> 26:41.240
If you're okay with it,
let's sign the contracts.

26:43.120 --> 26:44.520
The contract is fine.

26:47.840 --> 26:49.000
Okay.

26:52.600 --> 26:54.080
Thanks a lot, Ms. Bei.

26:54.160 --> 26:56.520
We'll deliver the items to your account

26:56.600 --> 26:58.160
at eight o'clock,
the night after tomorrow.

26:58.240 --> 27:00.520
It's been a pleasure. Goodbye.

27:21.200 --> 27:22.280
It's so crowded.

27:22.360 --> 27:24.040
We have to brace ourselves for the crowd.

27:24.120 --> 27:26.120
This is the last large job fair

27:26.200 --> 27:28.040
before we graduate.

27:28.600 --> 27:30.280
Many big corporations have come.

27:30.360 --> 27:33.120
It's the last job fair
before graduation.

27:33.200 --> 27:35.640
I know, we'll be leaving school soon.

27:35.720 --> 27:37.960
Who knows how many couples will break up?

27:38.360 --> 27:40.840
I'm so glad I'll be working nearby,
after I graduate.

27:44.640 --> 27:47.040
I was so clever today.

27:47.120 --> 27:50.360
I pitched the impossible ask,
then I compromised.

27:50.440 --> 27:53.200
He readily accepted my terms,
as predicted.

27:53.440 --> 27:56.640
I'll have graduation gifts for Lord
and the team, the day after tomorrow.

28:06.920 --> 28:08.560
He's not online, like he said,

28:08.880 --> 28:11.040
neither are Yugong and Houzi Jiu.

28:12.240 --> 28:13.600
Mo Zha Ta is!

28:28.760 --> 28:30.400
Ms. Weiwei?

28:34.920 --> 28:35.880
Mr. Girly?

28:42.840 --> 28:44.400
Who told you that nickname?

28:44.480 --> 28:46.400
I'm 180 cm tall, buffer than an ox,

28:46.480 --> 28:49.240
and a dark tan!
Who are you calling girly?

29:05.840 --> 29:08.040
Hao Mei missed you at the basketball game.

29:08.120 --> 29:09.200
He keeps asking to see you.

29:10.960 --> 29:13.400
- Hao Mei?
- Mo Zha Ta.

29:14.720 --> 29:19.640
Hao Mei? What a beautiful name.

29:19.920 --> 29:22.480
His mom dreamed that he was a girl,
on Mount Emei.

29:23.000 --> 29:25.800
He was named Hao Mei before he was born.

29:26.480 --> 29:29.640
Yugong and Houzi Jiu like to call him
"Girly" when they joke around.

29:34.720 --> 29:36.800
I can't implicate Lord.

29:37.040 --> 29:41.240
But I don't want to lie, either. I know!

29:42.360 --> 29:46.520
I saw Yugong and Houzi Jiu
at the basketball game the other day.

29:56.000 --> 29:57.800
How can you sell me out?

29:57.880 --> 29:59.520
You'll pay for running your mouths!

30:28.440 --> 30:30.520
I went for a real-life battle just now.

30:32.120 --> 30:34.000
Yugong? Houzi Jiu?

30:35.800 --> 30:38.720
They're covered in black and blue bruises,
begging for mercy.

30:39.080 --> 30:41.280
Don't worry. I didn't implicate you.

30:44.600 --> 30:49.280
See, I think you're quite lucky, actually.

30:49.600 --> 30:52.440
Wasn't your name inspired by Mount Emei?

30:53.440 --> 30:54.640
What if you're not named Hao Mei?

30:55.480 --> 30:57.920
Wouldn't you be named Hao E instead?

30:58.040 --> 31:01.680
Hao E sounds like "hungry" in Chinese.
That would be worse.

31:02.120 --> 31:03.920
Would I rather be called

31:04.000 --> 31:06.800
"hungry" or "girly" out on the street?

31:07.160 --> 31:09.960
I've chewed over that question
for many years.

31:10.680 --> 31:12.720
I could've been named Mount Hao.

31:19.400 --> 31:20.360
Mount Hao?

31:28.160 --> 31:29.920
The hairpin I'm making

31:30.000 --> 31:33.880
is only missing white jade and
quenched metal.

31:34.000 --> 31:36.640
When I get these two materials,
I can get to work.

31:37.200 --> 31:39.040
You're here at last, Weiwei!

31:39.120 --> 31:41.600
I thought you quit gaming,
like Clan Leader Diemeng.

31:42.680 --> 31:45.000
No, I've just been busy with exams.

31:45.320 --> 31:47.000
By the way, are you free now, Weiwei?

31:48.400 --> 31:49.240
What is it?

31:49.880 --> 31:51.240
Help me kill Underground Ghost Granny.

31:51.320 --> 31:54.120
It's the new boss in the instance dungeon.
I failed to crack it twice.

31:54.200 --> 31:55.040
Have you cracked it?

31:57.600 --> 32:01.120
I don't know how they'll be delivering
the rare monsters.

32:01.360 --> 32:04.360
I don't want to be caught
in the middle of offing a boss.

32:04.840 --> 32:06.720
Can we do it after eight? I'm a bit busy.

32:08.600 --> 32:10.520
Sure. I'll wait for you.

32:17.920 --> 32:19.480
Rare monsters...

32:19.560 --> 32:22.480
When I give the rare monsters to the guys,

32:22.560 --> 32:26.080
and we line up,
each with a rare monster,

32:26.160 --> 32:27.920
it'll be glorious!

32:32.080 --> 32:35.400
Mr. Girly, come over!
I'm giving you a rare monster.

32:44.320 --> 32:48.600
How did you know this rare monster
is perfect with my character, Mrs. Nai

32:48.680 --> 32:50.880
I've wanted it for a long time,
but I never got it.

32:52.600 --> 32:55.000
I knew it'd feel awesome
to share it with everyone.

32:57.320 --> 33:00.600
Where did you get this rare monster,
Mrs. Nai?

33:00.800 --> 33:02.800
That's extraordinary!

33:05.720 --> 33:09.480
From the company that bought the rights
to our "Girl Bandit Abducts Groom" video.

33:09.560 --> 33:11.880
All the main characters
in the video get one.

33:15.280 --> 33:19.320
They're so generous that they give out
rare monsters to the supporting cast?

33:19.400 --> 33:20.720
You asked for them, right?

33:24.120 --> 33:27.440
You don't have it spell it out.
Just be quietly touched.

33:31.840 --> 33:33.120
I'm so touched.

33:33.960 --> 33:37.240
Nai married well! He did indeed!

33:37.320 --> 33:39.240
We all benefit from his success.

33:47.880 --> 33:50.320
Mrs. Nai, there's something
you should know.

33:52.520 --> 33:53.480
What?

33:54.280 --> 33:59.080
Someone called our dorm today
to ask Nai out on a date.

34:05.320 --> 34:06.200
Um...

34:07.400 --> 34:11.719
It's true. I answered the phone.
It was a girl,

34:11.800 --> 34:13.840
but I heard Nai turn her down.

34:15.639 --> 34:17.120
Asked him out?

34:20.400 --> 34:22.760
Don't worry, Mrs. Nai, with me around,

34:22.840 --> 34:25.600
I'll never let Nai cheat on you.

34:27.719 --> 34:31.120
Dude, chill out.
Getting asked out is no big deal.

34:31.840 --> 34:34.600
Boys have asked me out all my life.

34:36.280 --> 34:39.040
Mr. Girly is too weak.

34:39.120 --> 34:40.719
He's always with Yugong and Houzi Jiu.

34:40.800 --> 34:43.120
What'll he do with such a weak threshold
for beat-downs?

34:50.040 --> 34:54.440
Nai just walked past behind me, Mrs. Nai,

34:57.840 --> 35:01.840
when you said
boys have asked you out all your life.

35:03.880 --> 35:06.960
No way! He said, he's busy,
and he won't be online tonight.

35:07.720 --> 35:08.920
He just got back.

35:15.520 --> 35:17.360
Now he's turning on his laptop.

35:41.200 --> 35:43.000
Thankfully I left in time.

35:43.280 --> 35:45.960
Wait, why should I log off?

35:46.040 --> 35:47.920
I was only joking, right?

35:48.400 --> 35:51.560
Doesn't logging off make it seem like
I had something to hide?

35:51.680 --> 35:54.160
No, I have to be open and honest.

35:54.240 --> 35:57.480
I have to be more than open and honest.

35:59.760 --> 36:01.000
I got kicked off line just now.

36:04.000 --> 36:07.080
Nai, your wife is a genius.

36:08.840 --> 36:10.000
Thanks.

36:11.600 --> 36:13.480
The campus internet is indeed unstable.

36:15.120 --> 36:16.840
Lord has great memory.

36:16.920 --> 36:19.080
Would he remember that for life?

36:19.400 --> 36:21.880
No, as the saying goes,

36:21.960 --> 36:24.560
"attack is the best form of defense."

36:25.600 --> 36:29.240
I heard someone called you
and asked you out today?

36:37.280 --> 36:38.880
I only got a call today,

36:38.960 --> 36:41.280
inviting me to play Guzheng
at the graduation gala.

36:44.200 --> 36:46.320
Yugong needs me. I should go...

36:53.280 --> 36:56.720
Mr. Girly, it's wrong to offer bad intel!

36:56.800 --> 36:58.760
You're doing me in.

37:01.560 --> 37:05.080
Don't worry, missus,
I never get asked out in all of my life.

37:06.920 --> 37:09.880
So what, if you never get asked out?

37:09.960 --> 37:12.400
Must you emphasize "all my life"?

37:14.920 --> 37:16.720
He must've done that on purpose.

37:16.920 --> 37:21.160
Wait, he said he's never been asked out?

37:21.960 --> 37:25.840
No way, I've seen someone
confess her love to you.

37:36.360 --> 37:37.560
When?

37:39.800 --> 37:41.160
Just this semester.

37:41.240 --> 37:42.800
Once, walking by our dorm,

37:42.880 --> 37:44.720
I saw a girl hand you a love letter.

37:47.280 --> 37:48.520
That seems to ring a bell.

37:49.320 --> 37:52.160
See? How can you say
no one's ever asked you out?

37:54.280 --> 37:56.960
She was probably just handing out a flier.

37:58.760 --> 37:59.600
No way!

38:01.680 --> 38:02.800
Why not?

38:02.880 --> 38:04.840
Would anyone confess her love
on the street?

38:04.920 --> 38:07.440
Has the missus had that experience?

38:07.520 --> 38:09.120
The missus sure is popular.

38:11.480 --> 38:15.120
No... When it becomes too frequent,
it can be troublesome.

38:15.200 --> 38:19.400
No... I mean, for these things,
it's quality over quantity.

38:19.480 --> 38:21.200
I'm all you need.

38:36.440 --> 38:37.520
Nai?

38:37.600 --> 38:39.920
Are you going to call
our department belle?

38:42.640 --> 38:47.360
What's going on? Nai didn't deny it.

38:47.840 --> 38:50.240
I can totally read his mind now.

38:50.320 --> 38:52.000
Aren't you impressed?

38:52.560 --> 38:56.680
Please! Nai can't hide
the lovey-dovey expression on his face.

38:56.760 --> 38:58.880
That's the unusual part!

38:59.200 --> 39:00.600
What's Nai usually like?

39:00.680 --> 39:05.280
He's cold and aloof,
with a blank expression all the time.

39:06.320 --> 39:07.680
Hou is right.

39:09.760 --> 39:12.960
This is bad of me.
I shouldn't be so sharp-tongued,

39:13.040 --> 39:15.280
like Yugong and the others.

39:15.480 --> 39:18.080
How will I face Lord tomorrow?
This is bad.

39:18.160 --> 39:21.760
I'll head out early tomorrow,
before he comes over.

39:27.160 --> 39:29.080
- Hello?
- It's me.

39:34.080 --> 39:37.240
- You logged off, too?
- No.

39:38.840 --> 39:41.880
The campus internet is awful today.
I got kicked off, too.

39:44.320 --> 39:47.080
Does it keep you up at night, Lord,

39:47.160 --> 39:49.000
if you don't tease me a few times a day?

39:51.000 --> 39:54.320
Weiwei, I'm happy.

39:56.200 --> 39:59.760
Is he happy because of what I said?

40:02.480 --> 40:05.880
For the video licensing contract,

40:05.960 --> 40:08.120
I asked the company for rare monsters.

40:09.560 --> 40:11.120
Hao Mei told me.

40:12.440 --> 40:15.200
I asked for five.
I'll give you yours soon.

40:17.760 --> 40:19.840
I asked for a little tiger.

40:19.920 --> 40:22.520
Yours is a little tiger, too,

40:22.720 --> 40:24.320
but they're the opposite sex.

40:26.560 --> 40:27.680
So...

40:29.080 --> 40:31.680
So, we'll raise them.

40:31.760 --> 40:33.280
Let them breed.

40:33.400 --> 40:36.240
They might produce a sixth rare monster.

40:37.600 --> 40:41.280
Okay, I'll ask my tiger next time,

40:41.480 --> 40:42.480
if he's willing.

40:44.240 --> 40:45.520
Why do you have to ask?

40:45.600 --> 40:47.920
There's only one female tiger
in the entire game.

40:48.000 --> 40:49.240
Why would he refuse?

40:51.880 --> 40:54.640
That makes sense. I'm sure he will.

40:57.720 --> 40:58.720
Are you free now?

41:01.520 --> 41:04.520
Will you log on and help my friend
fight a boss?

41:08.320 --> 41:09.720
Bye-bye now.

41:23.280 --> 41:25.000
Why did you log off, Weiwei?

41:27.600 --> 41:29.040
Likely kicked off.

41:32.000 --> 41:34.040
I thought you stood me up.

41:34.920 --> 41:37.720
No... How many spots do you have?

41:37.800 --> 41:38.760
I'll bring a master player.

41:39.760 --> 41:42.440
I haven't invited anyone.
You guys should just come.

41:43.480 --> 41:46.720
I'm here. I just got rid of
a bunch of onlookers.

41:50.480 --> 41:53.080
Yixiao Naihe is helping me off a boss?

41:54.360 --> 41:57.200
Fighting with him is a thrill.
Let him take command.

41:59.440 --> 42:00.360
Okay.

42:01.080 --> 42:04.240
I've never encountered an underworld boss.
You, Naihe?

42:04.560 --> 42:07.000
- No.
- I'll check the website.

42:07.080 --> 42:10.120
It's okay.
Get another long-distance attacker.

42:10.240 --> 42:11.440
It'll be faster.

42:12.120 --> 42:15.280
Okay, I'll put a call out to the clan.
Someone will come.

42:16.960 --> 42:18.760
Anyone want to off Underworld Granny?

42:18.840 --> 42:20.760
Two spots, one shooter and one anything.

42:22.040 --> 42:24.360
Two spots?
Yaoyao and I will be right over.

44:53.720 --> 44:56.160
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
